29:18.820 --> 29:21.914
You're sure?

29:21.960 --> 29:24.952
Yeah, I'm sure.

29:27.130 --> 29:28.119
(door closes)

29:31.930 --> 29:34.091
Watson...

29:34.140 --> 29:36.859
how was your day?

29:36.900 --> 29:38.333
Whose computer is that?

29:38.370 --> 29:39.564
It's Trent Annunzio's.

29:39.610 --> 29:41.339
Borrowing it.

29:41.380 --> 29:43.029
Why?

29:43.080 --> 29:45.105
Because...

29:45.150 --> 29:47.345
I strongly suspect that
it may once have contained

29:47.380 --> 29:50.269
evidence that would prove
Annunzio abused his wife.

29:50.320 --> 29:53.118
I thought the hard drive
may have been swapped out,

29:53.150 --> 29:56.051
but that doesn't appear
to be the case.

29:56.090 --> 29:59.287
You said this morning
that she was the one

29:59.330 --> 30:02.254
who hired Raul Ramirez
to kill him.

30:02.300 --> 30:04.222
I did.

30:04.270 --> 30:07.159
Then why are you looking for
evidence to help her?

30:07.200 --> 30:10.590
Because, upon further
examination of the facts,

30:10.640 --> 30:13.302
I now have reason to believe
that I was wrong,

30:13.340 --> 30:16.832
and that in accusing her, I may
have inadvertently positioned

30:16.880 --> 30:19.371
the United Stated Immigration
and Customs Enforcement Agency

30:19.410 --> 30:22.208
to separate an innocent woman
from her infant daughter

30:22.250 --> 30:24.912
on a very permanent basis.

30:28.990 --> 30:31.424
That tea that you made
the other day,

30:31.460 --> 30:34.020
could you make some more of it?

30:37.300 --> 30:39.461
I keep asking myself,

30:39.500 --> 30:41.639
why would she tell us about
her husband's brutality

30:41.670 --> 30:43.331
