30:43.370 --> 30:45.099
that she could show
us some proof?

30:45.140 --> 30:47.301
You think someone
wiped his computer for him?

30:47.340 --> 30:49.376
It's hard to say.

30:49.410 --> 30:51.275
I haven't exactly been
at my best lately.

30:51.310 --> 30:52.504
Well, you were right

30:52.550 --> 30:54.245
about Liam--
that pendant I gave him,

30:54.280 --> 30:56.214
it was stolen.
He told me this morning.

30:56.250 --> 30:58.946
I spent the rest
of the day visiting
pawnshops in Queens

30:58.990 --> 31:00.389
until I found it.

31:00.420 --> 31:02.911
The owner knew the kid
who brought it in,

31:02.960 --> 31:05.428
so once the police find him,
they're gonna let Liam go.

31:05.460 --> 31:08.896
Mm. Well done, Watson.

31:08.930 --> 31:12.093
Perhaps you should take the
reins on the Annunzio case.

31:16.370 --> 31:19.931
I didn't tell you
the whole story.

31:19.970 --> 31:21.972
Liam's not an ex-client.

31:22.010 --> 31:24.149
He's just... an ex.

31:27.010 --> 31:30.070
You were romantically involved;
you just weren't his companion.

31:30.120 --> 31:32.315
Imamm_
on an ER rotation

31:32.350 --> 31:34.159
back when I was
still a resident.

31:34.190 --> 31:37.057
Some lady got
her purse snatched
in front of him.

31:37.090 --> 31:38.421
He tackled the guy,
the guy smashed his skull

31:38.460 --> 31:40.280
