31:40.330 --> 31:42.457
I gave him 39 stitches.

31:42.500 --> 31:44.525
Was he already using?

31:44.570 --> 31:48.097
No.

31:48.140 --> 31:50.165
No, that came later.

31:52.340 --> 31:55.537
I hosted an intervention,
I drove him to rehab.

31:55.580 --> 31:58.174
He was better when he came out,

31:58.210 --> 31:59.973
but only for a little while.

32:00.010 --> 32:04.185
Everything that followed
is typically what follows.

32:04.220 --> 32:06.984
A lot of lies,

32:07.020 --> 32:08.556
heartbreak.

32:08.590 --> 32:10.319
Anyway, the upside was that

32:10.360 --> 32:13.989
I learned a lot about how
to deal with people like him.

32:14.030 --> 32:16.055
So when I left medicine,

32:16.100 --> 32:18.466
companionship seemed like
a pretty natural fit.

32:18.500 --> 32:21.492
(phone chimes)

32:21.540 --> 32:24.566
Hmm.

32:24.610 --> 32:27.408
It's the autopsy report
on Trent Annunzio.

32:27.440 --> 32:29.328
The ME found dried
chrysanthemum

32:29.380 --> 32:31.041
and mulberry leaf in
his stomach contents.

32:31.080 --> 32:32.342
Oh, those are both...

32:32.380 --> 32:34.439
Medicinal Chinese herbs.
Yes, well aware.

32:34.480 --> 32:37.643
This particular combination
is used to treat eye pain.

32:37.680 --> 32:38.715
How did you know that?

32:38.750 --> 32:41.287
I may have done some research
into the efficacy

32:41.320 --> 32:43.254
of Chinese medicine
after the herbs that you gave me

32:43.290 --> 32:45.383
had a positive correlation
with my recovery.

32:45.430 --> 32:50.299
Aanay, point is, this could
hardly be a coincidence.

32:50.330 --> 32:54.391
He was shot in both eyes while
self-medicating for eye pain.

32:54.440 --> 32:58.308
I noticed something
back at his apartment.

32:58.340 --> 33:00.604
There was a photograph of him
and his students.

33:00.640 --> 33:03.677
Everyone in it had, um,

33:03.710 --> 33:06.304
red eye from the camera flash
except for him.

33:06.350 --> 33:08.477
I didn't give it much thought,
but it's possible

33:08.520 --> 33:11.045
that something was blocking
his tapetum lucidum.

33:11.090 --> 33:12.341
The reflective part
of the retina.

33:12.390 --> 33:13.482
Such as?

33:13.520 --> 33:16.182
Best guess would be a melanoma.

33:16.220 --> 33:19.121
We need to get
to the coroner's office.

33:19.160 --> 33:22.755
I think I know who arranged
Trent Annunzio's murder.

33:22.800 --> 33:25.064
GREGSON:
You want to tell me
what I'm looking at?

33:25.100 --> 33:26.419
Melanoma cells.

33:26.470 --> 33:27.767
The medical examiner

33:27.800 --> 33:29.665
