his wife said he was.

33:58.600 --> 34:01.433
He tortured her, physically,
psychologically.

34:01.470 --> 34:03.461
Forced her to perform
sexual acts

34:03.500 --> 34:05.104
in front of a camera.

34:05.140 --> 34:06.562
Now imagine he discovers
that his favorite

34:06.610 --> 34:09.431
plaything slash punching bag
is having an affair

34:09.480 --> 34:13.143
with his teaching assistant,
Mr. O'Brien.

34:13.180 --> 34:17.446
A man like Annunzio, prone
to deviousness and violence,

34:17.480 --> 34:20.313
no doubt started
plotting his revenge.

34:20.350 --> 34:22.784
Problem was,
he began to experience

34:22.820 --> 34:25.186
this-this terrible eye pain.

34:25.230 --> 34:27.585
He consults a doctor.

34:27.630 --> 34:28.824
He learned his fate.

34:28.860 --> 34:30.350
Rotten luck, or

34:30.400 --> 34:32.459
instant karma... doesn't matter.

34:32.500 --> 34:35.833
Annunzio was... was reeling.

34:35.870 --> 34:37.462
All he had left

34:37.500 --> 34:40.105
was his intellect
and his anger.

34:40.140 --> 34:42.108
So he devised a plan

34:42.140 --> 34:43.505
that would not
only exact revenge

34:43.540 --> 34:45.440
upon his wife and her lover,

34:45.480 --> 34:49.576
but also deliver_ him from
a slow and agoni2ing death.

34:49.620 --> 34:52.612
He found Raul Ramirez,

34:52.650 --> 34:54.208
and he hired him

34:54.260 --> 34:56.114
to be his very own executioner.

34:56.160 --> 34:58.628
After that,

34:58.660 --> 35:01.151
it was just a matter of gaining
access to O'Brien's apartment.

35:01.200 --> 35:03.259
Probably with a stolen key.
Mm.

35:03.300 --> 35:05.894
He planted evidence
that would implicate O'Brien--

35:05.930 --> 35:07.864
the phone used
to contact Ramirez--

35:07.900 --> 35:10.460
and then he writes
a recommendation

35:10.500 --> 35:12.639
that he knows would demonstrate

35:12.670 --> 35:14.501
that O'Brien
has motive for murder.

35:14.540 --> 35:16.405
Now all that's
left to do is to

35:16.440 --> 35:18.544
destroy any evidence that might

35:18.580 --> 35:20.275
unravel his plans:

35:20.310 --> 35:21.572
Firstly,
the incriminating videos

35:21.620 --> 35:22.848
he keeps on his computer.

35:22.880 --> 35:25.587
Secondly, his eyes.

35:25.620 --> 35:29.750
They're proof that he faced
a long, horrible illness.

35:29.790 --> 35:32.258
And he can't risk anyone
discovering his condition.

35:32.290 --> 35:34.429
There may be immediate
questions asked

35:34.460 --> 35:36.451
as to whether he arranged
his own murder.

35:36.500 --> 35:38.320
The only thing
he cannot account for

35:38.370 --> 35:41.567
is the unpredictable nature
of his would-be assassin.

35:41.600 --> 35:43.295
Ramirez was supposed to kill him

35:43.340 --> 35:44.739
when he was on
his way to his car.

35:44.770 --> 35:46.635
Instead, he kills him

35:46.670 --> 35:48.570
ahead of schedule, and makes it
look like a robbery gone wrong.

35:48.610 --> 35:49.770
Now, that's the last thing

35:49.810 --> 35:51.778
that he wanted.

35:51.810 --> 35:55.268
Annunzio wanted all fingers
pointed squarely at O'Brien.

35:56.850 --> 36:00.581
It's not a perfect theory,
Captain, but it fits.

36:00.620 --> 36:01.882
I think that Annunzio's wife

36:01.920 --> 36:05.629
and Mr. O'Brien
may well be innocent.

36:05.660 --> 36:07.685
Well, let's pretend for
a second that you're right.

36:07.730 --> 36:10.358
We can't just
cut O'Brien loose

36:10.400 --> 36:11.697
based on a theory.

36:11.730 --> 36:13.698
Not with the phone in evidence,

36:13.730 --> 36:14.958
and a signed confession.

36:15.000 --> 36:16.695
What about Jun?

36:16.740 --> 36:18.662
We didn't have enough
to hold her.

36:18.710 --> 36:20.234
We cut her loose to I.C.E.

36:20.270 --> 36:22.670
They already started
deportation proceedings.

36:22.710 --> 36:24.439
Now, I'm sorry,

36:24.480 --> 36:26.869
if you think this is all
part of a master plan

36:26.910 --> 36:28.548
concocted by the victim,

36:28.580 --> 36:31.743
then it's a damn good one.

36:39.730 --> 36:42.824
(traffic sounds, horn honks)

36:42.860 --> 36:46.364
(sighs)

36:46.400 --> 36:47.594
This is new.

36:47.630 --> 36:49.734
Old data, new location.

36:49.770 --> 36:51.863
Thought it might
jar something loose.

36:51.910 --> 36:53.605
Did you get
any sleep last night?

36:53.640 --> 36:54.868
Hard to sleep

36:54.910 --> 36:56.468
knowing a psychopath
may have managed

36:56.510 --> 36:58.273
to ruin two lives
from beyond the grave.

36:58.310 --> 37:00.744
Well, for some us,
I suppose.

37:01.850 --> 37:03.340
Well, I am gonna

37:03.380 --> 37:05.439
have to take a shower
before I go to Rikers.

37:05.490 --> 37:07.708
Carry on.

37:09.020 --> 37:10.612
Oh, you weren't kidding
when you said

37:10.660 --> 37:12.480
O'Brien and Ramirez
