38:00.770 --> 38:02.772
You type in O'Brien's address,

38:02.810 --> 38:05.278
find the nearest deviant.

38:06.510 --> 38:07.943
Only he wasn't
the nearest one.

38:07.980 --> 38:10.346
There's another guy
